1
00:00:42,792 --> 00:00:45,962
LIKE FLOWERS IN SAND

2
00:00:47,005 --> 00:00:48,715
<i>Oh Du-sik.</i>

3
00:00:49,174 --> 00:00:51,968
<i>Lahir 23 Agustus, 1992.</i>

4
00:00:53,928 --> 00:00:56,347
<i>Dia putri tunggal dari Juara Oh Jun,</i>

5
00:00:56,431 --> 00:00:59,017
<i>pendominasi</i> ssireum
<i>tahun '80-an dan '90-an.</i>

6
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:02,228
<i>Du-sik spesial dalam beberapa hal.</i>

7
00:01:03,605 --> 00:01:06,024
- Apa itu?
- Pegang saja ini sebentar.

8
00:01:07,108 --> 00:01:08,902
Kenapa aku?

9
00:01:08,985 --> 00:01:13,281
<i>Pertama, dia pemimpin</i>
<i>semua anak-anak di desa.</i>

10
00:01:13,364 --> 00:01:16,576
<i>Dia dikenal sebagai anak</i>
<i>yang riang dan kuat.</i>

11
00:01:16,659 --> 00:01:19,204
- Mungkin dia menangkap kadal.
- Kadal?

12
00:01:20,330 --> 00:01:22,373
- Kau dapat kadal?
- Biar kulihat.

13
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:26,419
<i>Yang utama, dia tak kenal takut.</i>

14
00:01:34,886 --> 00:01:37,847
"Ayo ke hutan.

15
00:01:38,973 --> 00:01:41,768
Ayo ke hutan, mengambil serpihan bulan."

16
00:01:43,895 --> 00:01:46,731
Penyair Yoon Dong-ju
terus merefleksikan diri.

17
00:01:46,815 --> 00:01:47,899
Oper ini.

18
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:51,528
Dia malu tidak lebih aktif terlibat

19
00:01:51,611 --> 00:01:55,240
dalam perjuangan kemerdekaan
saat Korea dijajah Jepang.

20
00:01:56,407 --> 00:01:57,951
Keinginannya untuk merdeka

21
00:01:58,034 --> 00:01:59,327
- dan refleksi…
<i>- Hei.</i>

22
00:01:59,410 --> 00:02:03,123
<i>Kau terlihat sangat jelek</i>
<i>terkena sinar matahari.</i>

23
00:02:11,464 --> 00:02:14,592
<i>Serta dia sangat mudah marah.</i>

24
00:02:14,676 --> 00:02:18,638
<i>Seluruh anak lelaki di kota</i>
<i>pernah dipukul Du-sik minimal sekali.</i>

25
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:27,647
Ayolah, Du-sik. Hentikan.

26
00:02:34,612 --> 00:02:35,530
<i>Dan…</i>

27
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,741
Hei, Kim Baek-du.

28
00:02:39,242 --> 00:02:42,912
Jangan sampai kalah oleh seorang gadis.
Itu memalukan.

29
00:02:44,247 --> 00:02:47,208
- Hati-hati. Dia hebat.
- Ayo, Du-sik!

30
00:02:47,292 --> 00:02:48,418
Du-sik!

31
00:02:48,501 --> 00:02:52,505
- Du-sik!
- Du-sik akan menang!

32
00:02:54,132 --> 00:02:55,383
Ayo, Du-sik!

33
00:02:57,218 --> 00:02:58,720
Semangat, Du-sik!

34
00:02:59,596 --> 00:03:02,891
Ayo, Du-sik!

35
00:03:22,035 --> 00:03:25,997
<i>Bisa dibilang, dia pegulat</i> ssireum
<i>terbaik di antara kami.</i>

36
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:35,465
EPISODE 2
ADA SESUATU TENTANG OH DU-SIK

37
00:03:37,425 --> 00:03:38,551
Benar, ya?

38
00:03:38,635 --> 00:03:39,886
Kau Oh Du-sik.

39
00:03:42,847 --> 00:03:44,432
{\an8}Itu sungguh kau?

40
00:03:44,515 --> 00:03:46,893
{\an8}Sungguh, Du-sik, teganya kau…

41
00:03:46,976 --> 00:03:49,938
{\an8}Hei! Teganya kau melakukan ini padaku.

42
00:03:50,021 --> 00:03:52,398
{\an8}Aku terus menunggumu menghubungi!

43
00:03:52,482 --> 00:03:55,151
{\an8}Setidaknya tinggalkan pesan sebelum pergi,

44
00:03:55,235 --> 00:03:56,402
{\an8}atau menelepon!

45
00:03:56,486 --> 00:03:58,613
{\an8}Kau tahu alamat dan nomor ponselku.

46
00:03:58,696 --> 00:04:01,157
{\an8}Kau seharusnya menghubungiku jika mau!

47
00:04:01,241 --> 00:04:03,743
{\an8}Teganya kau menjauhiku begitu saja.

48
00:04:03,826 --> 00:04:06,120
{\an8}Kau kejam sekali.

49
00:04:07,664 --> 00:04:11,042
{\an8}Intinya, kau kembali.
Itulah yang penting, 'kan?

50
00:04:12,210 --> 00:04:13,419
{\an8}Selamat datang, Du-sik.

51
00:04:17,507 --> 00:04:19,133
Ada apa, Du-sik?

52
00:04:20,051 --> 00:04:23,179
Ayolah. Reaksi macam apa itu?

53
00:04:23,263 --> 00:04:24,973
Kau tak senang bertemu aku lagi?

54
00:04:25,056 --> 00:04:26,516
Kau tak merindukanku?

55
00:04:27,016 --> 00:04:29,394
- Dengar…
- Aku sangat merindukanmu.

56
00:04:33,314 --> 00:04:34,899
<i>Du-sik itu perempuan?</i>

57
00:04:35,566 --> 00:04:36,526
Ya.

58
00:04:37,735 --> 00:04:40,238
Kenapa aku berpikir dia pria?

59
00:04:40,321 --> 00:04:42,532
Tak ada yang bilang Du-sik pria.

60
00:04:43,449 --> 00:04:45,368
Kau benar.

61
00:04:45,451 --> 00:04:49,330
Kurasa kupikir dia pria
karena namanya Du-sik.

62
00:04:49,414 --> 00:04:53,710
Ya, namanya. Mayoritas kisahnya pun
soal membuat masalah, jadi…

63
00:04:53,793 --> 00:04:54,794
Begitu rupanya.

64
00:04:55,628 --> 00:04:58,381
- Jadi, Du-sik itu wanita.
- Ya.

65
00:04:58,464 --> 00:05:01,759
Itu sebabnya dia banyak menyebut
nama Du-sik hari itu.

66
00:05:01,843 --> 00:05:03,594
- Apa?
- Apa?

67
00:05:03,678 --> 00:05:04,804
Bukan apa-apa.

68
00:05:06,097 --> 00:05:09,809
Jadi, bagaimana kisah Du-sik?

69
00:05:11,269 --> 00:05:12,729
Ayolah. Jangan begini.

70
00:05:12,812 --> 00:05:15,106
Apa karena aku bukan dari sini?

71
00:05:15,189 --> 00:05:19,235
Tidak, bukan begitu.
Aku sungguh tak tahu banyak soal itu.

72
00:05:20,278 --> 00:05:23,114
Hanya Tae-baek, Jun, dan Du-sik
yang tahu kejadiannya.

73
00:05:25,283 --> 00:05:28,578
Jadi, jangan bicarakan Du-sik
di tempat lain.

74
00:05:29,787 --> 00:05:30,621
Kenapa tidak?

75
00:05:31,622 --> 00:05:33,624
Kejadiannya bukan hal bagus.

76
00:05:36,586 --> 00:05:37,712
Aku bukan dia.

77
00:05:37,795 --> 00:05:39,172
Apa katamu, Du-sik?

78
00:05:40,798 --> 00:05:42,592
Kubilang, aku bukan dia.

79
00:05:42,675 --> 00:05:43,593
Apa maksudmu?

80
00:05:43,676 --> 00:05:47,180
Kau pasti mengira aku orang lain.
Aku bukan Oh Du-sik.

81
00:05:49,057 --> 00:05:52,143
Apa? Tunggu. Tahan sebentar. Hei.

82
00:05:52,226 --> 00:05:54,937
Kau bukan Oh Du-sik?

83
00:05:55,772 --> 00:05:56,731
Lalu siapa kau?

84
00:06:00,318 --> 00:06:01,444
Maksudku…

85
00:06:02,195 --> 00:06:04,405
Kalau begitu, kau siapa, Bu?

86
00:06:04,489 --> 00:06:05,990
Aku harus memberitahumu?

87
00:06:07,325 --> 00:06:08,743
Bisa tolong pergi?

88
00:06:08,826 --> 00:06:11,204
Ini tindakan masuk tanpa izin.

89
00:06:11,287 --> 00:06:12,121
Apa?

90
00:06:16,667 --> 00:06:17,835
Tapi…

91
00:06:20,296 --> 00:06:21,964
Aku yakin dia Du-sik.

92
00:06:24,258 --> 00:06:25,510
Bola Salju.

93
00:06:26,886 --> 00:06:28,554
Bola Salju?

94
00:06:30,515 --> 00:06:32,391
Bola Salju, di mana kau?

95
00:06:41,651 --> 00:06:42,985
Bola Salju.

96
00:06:44,487 --> 00:06:45,696
Bola Salju.

97
00:06:49,492 --> 00:06:51,869
Kau di sini? Bola Salju!

98
00:06:53,246 --> 00:06:54,622
Bola Salju!

99
00:06:55,748 --> 00:06:58,000
Kau tak pikir ada yang mencurigakan?

100
00:06:58,668 --> 00:07:00,920
Bau apa ini?

101
00:07:01,003 --> 00:07:03,047
Astaga, itu kotoran.

102
00:07:03,923 --> 00:07:05,550
- Sial.
- Apa-apaan ini?

103
00:07:05,633 --> 00:07:09,720
Bola Salju, anak nakal itu.
Dia pasti sembunyi di suatu tempat.

104
00:07:10,346 --> 00:07:12,265
Maksudku, kasus di waduk itu.

105
00:07:12,348 --> 00:07:14,725
Ada banyak hal aneh di sana.

106
00:07:14,809 --> 00:07:16,436
Astaga, sudahlah.

107
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:21,482
Rumornya, arwahnya masih berkeliaran
di dunia ini karena kau.

108
00:07:21,566 --> 00:07:23,484
Jika masih berkeliaran di sini,

109
00:07:23,568 --> 00:07:26,696
pasti karena dia merasa dizalimi,
bukan karena aku.

110
00:07:26,779 --> 00:07:29,365
Melihat kematiannya ditutupi seperti ini.

111
00:07:29,449 --> 00:07:31,075
Astaga.

112
00:07:31,159 --> 00:07:32,994
Sungguh, bukankah itu aneh?

113
00:07:33,077 --> 00:07:36,247
Kenapa dia mati di kota
yang tak berkaitan dengannya?

114
00:07:36,330 --> 00:07:38,916
Dan kenapa tenggelam di waduk

115
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,461
yang tak banyak diketahui warga desa?

116
00:07:41,544 --> 00:07:46,132
Hei, hidup dan mati adalah takdir.

117
00:07:46,215 --> 00:07:48,593
Tak ada yang aneh soal itu.

118
00:07:48,676 --> 00:07:51,637
Diam saja dan carilah Bola Salju.

119
00:07:51,721 --> 00:07:53,181
Bagaimana dengan CCTV?

120
00:07:53,806 --> 00:07:57,518
Para petugas dari Seoul mengumpulkan
semua CCTV di kota.

121
00:07:57,602 --> 00:08:00,688
Kenapa mereka lakukan itu?
Takkan ada tontonan seru.

122
00:08:02,607 --> 00:08:03,816
Aku yakin itu.

123
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:07,403
Ada yang belum terungkap.
Itu bukan kematian tak disengaja.

124
00:08:07,487 --> 00:08:08,529
Lantas bagaimana?

125
00:08:08,613 --> 00:08:11,157
Apa yang bisa kau lakukan soal itu?

126
00:08:11,741 --> 00:08:13,910
- Akan kucari tahu.
- Sulit dipercaya.

127
00:08:13,993 --> 00:08:16,370
Meski rekaman CCTV-nya hilang,

128
00:08:16,954 --> 00:08:18,789
jika ada kemauan, ada jalan.

129
00:08:18,873 --> 00:08:21,792
Jangan membuat masalah.

130
00:08:21,876 --> 00:08:25,546
Begini, mencari anjing
yang kabur seperti ini

131
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:27,048
bukanlah keahlianku…

132
00:08:27,131 --> 00:08:30,760
Bola Salju!

133
00:08:31,969 --> 00:08:33,930
Bola Salju!

134
00:08:34,514 --> 00:08:36,766
Bola Salju!

135
00:08:40,686 --> 00:08:41,687
Hei. Cepat!

136
00:08:41,771 --> 00:08:43,689
- Bola Salju!
- Cepat!

137
00:08:44,649 --> 00:08:46,025
Astaga.

138
00:08:46,817 --> 00:08:49,946
- Bakatnya alami.
- Ayo! Kemarilah!

139
00:08:50,905 --> 00:08:52,031
Bola Salju!

140
00:08:53,199 --> 00:08:54,450
Rumah itu?

141
00:08:54,534 --> 00:08:57,036
Bukankah sudah lama kosong?

142
00:08:57,119 --> 00:08:59,497
- Benar. Tapi tampaknya…
- Bola Salju!

143
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:01,415
ada yang datang kemarin sore.

144
00:09:01,499 --> 00:09:02,875
Kemarin sore?

145
00:09:02,959 --> 00:09:04,252
- Astaga.
- Lihat.

146
00:09:04,335 --> 00:09:05,545
Apa itu?

147
00:09:05,628 --> 00:09:08,839
Larilah, Bola Salju!

148
00:09:10,007 --> 00:09:12,426
- Anjing itu melatihnya.
- Ayo.

149
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:13,844
Kau mengejarnya lagi?

150
00:09:14,387 --> 00:09:15,721
Astaga, berhentilah!

151
00:09:18,015 --> 00:09:18,891
Hei!

152
00:09:21,185 --> 00:09:22,603
Berhenti!

153
00:09:55,219 --> 00:09:57,555
Jadi, berandal ini masuk tim apa?

154
00:09:58,389 --> 00:10:01,183
Entahlah. Kudengar
dia bertemu banyak orang.

155
00:10:01,267 --> 00:10:02,893
Dia akan pilih bayaran terbesar.

156
00:10:02,977 --> 00:10:05,855
Bagaimana Pak Hong?
Dia tak akan coba menahannya?

157
00:10:05,938 --> 00:10:08,149
Yang benar saja.

158
00:10:08,232 --> 00:10:11,027
Dia pasti menikmati situasi ini.

159
00:10:11,861 --> 00:10:15,990
Dia selalu ingin membubarkan
tim <i>ssireum</i> itu.

160
00:10:16,073 --> 00:10:18,993
Dia pasti belum membubarkannya
karena Lim Dong-seok.

161
00:10:19,577 --> 00:10:22,913
Ini artinya tim <i>ssireum</i> itu
sungguh akan dibubarkan?

162
00:10:23,873 --> 00:10:26,751
Kenapa kau tak temui dan bicara
dengan Pak Hong?

163
00:10:26,834 --> 00:10:28,919
Rasanya tidak tepat

164
00:10:29,003 --> 00:10:31,589
mendiktenya soal tim yang berisi putraku…

165
00:10:32,298 --> 00:10:33,799
Tapi Baek-du pensiun.

166
00:10:35,676 --> 00:10:37,720
Apa? Itu yang dia katakan.

167
00:10:37,803 --> 00:10:41,849
Dia bilang kepada semua akan pensiun
jika tak menang kejuaraan itu.

168
00:10:41,932 --> 00:10:44,226
Ayolah. Keputusan juri kontroversial.

169
00:10:44,310 --> 00:10:46,812
Baek-du bisa dibilang pemenangnya.

170
00:10:46,896 --> 00:10:49,982
Pokoknya, dia tidak menang.
Itulah faktanya.

171
00:10:50,066 --> 00:10:52,401
- Hei!
- Apa katamu tadi?

172
00:10:54,195 --> 00:10:56,572
Bagaimana Baek-du? Dia baik-baik saja?

173
00:10:56,656 --> 00:10:59,367
Dia pasti kecewa. Dia mau makan?

174
00:10:59,450 --> 00:11:02,662
Dia pasti merasa sedih.
Pasti tak nafsu makan.

175
00:11:03,663 --> 00:11:06,248
Suruh dia kemari.

176
00:11:06,332 --> 00:11:07,625
Kubelikan daging…

177
00:11:07,708 --> 00:11:12,713
Baek-du makan besar setelahnya
dan pergi pagi-pagi sekali.

178
00:11:16,926 --> 00:11:19,303
Identitasmu dikenali jika begitu.

179
00:11:23,808 --> 00:11:25,184
Sial.

180
00:11:31,524 --> 00:11:33,275
Kenapa kau kemari sepagi ini?

181
00:11:33,359 --> 00:11:35,903
Hei, Seok-hui. Bisakah kau…

182
00:11:36,779 --> 00:11:39,573
Baumu seperti kotoran.

183
00:11:39,657 --> 00:11:41,242
Kau buang air di celana?

184
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:43,619
Bicara dan pergilah.

185
00:11:43,702 --> 00:11:46,580
Aku lelah setelah berlarian,
sulit berdiri.

186
00:11:47,164 --> 00:11:48,958
Seok-hui, aku ingin tanya…

187
00:11:49,041 --> 00:11:52,253
Begini, hal itu…

188
00:11:52,336 --> 00:11:53,796
- Kau bisa…
- Pergilah.

189
00:11:53,879 --> 00:11:56,549
Apa? Hei, aku baru mau bicara.

190
00:11:56,632 --> 00:11:58,592
Langsung ke intinya saja.

191
00:11:58,676 --> 00:12:02,263
Begini, hal yang kalian lakukan di sini…

192
00:12:02,346 --> 00:12:04,598
Hei, tunggu.

193
00:12:05,599 --> 00:12:07,059
Periksa latar belakang.

194
00:12:07,601 --> 00:12:10,104
- Bisa lakukan itu?
- Latar belakang?

195
00:12:10,604 --> 00:12:11,897
Kenapa tiba-tiba?

196
00:12:12,565 --> 00:12:14,191
Ini…

197
00:12:14,275 --> 00:12:16,610
- Kau ditipu?
- Tidak, bukan hal itu.

198
00:12:16,694 --> 00:12:19,196
Aku tahu kau akan ditipu suatu hari.

199
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:21,574
- Kubilang, bukan.
- Bukan itu?

200
00:12:22,074 --> 00:12:23,117
Lalu apa?

201
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:25,202
Katakan saja. Bisa atau tidak?

202
00:12:25,286 --> 00:12:28,539
Tidak, kami lakukan itu
hanya untuk pekerjaan.

203
00:12:29,415 --> 00:12:32,168
Kenapa? Ada apa?
Kau mau latar belakang siapa?

204
00:12:37,006 --> 00:12:37,882
Wanita itu?

205
00:12:39,091 --> 00:12:42,011
Kau mau aku periksa apa dia Du-sik?

206
00:12:42,094 --> 00:12:43,095
Ya.

207
00:12:43,888 --> 00:12:46,056
Apa harus kulakukan?

208
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:48,517
Aku bisa tahu hanya dengan melihatnya.

209
00:12:48,601 --> 00:12:49,518
Begitukah?

210
00:12:50,019 --> 00:12:51,395
Lalu apa pendapatmu?

211
00:12:51,896 --> 00:12:54,773
Kau gila? Dia tampak sangat berbeda.

212
00:12:54,857 --> 00:12:56,108
Apa? Itu bukan dia?

213
00:12:56,692 --> 00:12:58,444
Kau lupa rupa Du-sik?

214
00:12:58,527 --> 00:12:59,862
Dia mirip Du-sik.

215
00:12:59,945 --> 00:13:02,198
Astaga, kau pasti hilang akal.

216
00:13:02,281 --> 00:13:06,410
Hei, Du-sik banyak memukuliku
karena menyebutnya jelek saat kita kecil.

217
00:13:06,494 --> 00:13:08,329
Kita suka melebihkan masa lalu,

218
00:13:08,412 --> 00:13:10,789
tapi kau seperti menulis ulang kenangan.

219
00:13:10,873 --> 00:13:13,667
- Jadi, itu bukan dia?
- Tentu saja bukan.

220
00:13:13,751 --> 00:13:17,338
Pikirkan saja.

221
00:13:17,421 --> 00:13:18,756
Jika kau Du-sik…

222
00:13:20,758 --> 00:13:22,343
kau mau kembali kemari?

223
00:13:26,138 --> 00:13:27,723
Kau tahu?

224
00:13:28,557 --> 00:13:31,519
Du-sik lebih jelek
saat terkena sinar matahari.

225
00:13:34,021 --> 00:13:35,606
Kau yakin itu bukan dia?

226
00:13:45,199 --> 00:13:46,116
Pergilah.

227
00:13:47,117 --> 00:13:48,536
Kumohon, pergilah.

228
00:13:54,291 --> 00:13:55,125
Halo?

229
00:13:56,669 --> 00:13:57,545
Ya.

230
00:13:59,463 --> 00:14:02,466
