00:16:30,489 --> 00:16:33,075
Pergilah. Jangan mendekat.

287
00:16:34,952 --> 00:16:36,495
Kau mau ke suatu tempat?

288
00:16:36,578 --> 00:16:38,872
Ya, tim terburu-buru meneleponku.

289
00:16:38,956 --> 00:16:41,709
Begitu rupanya. Kalau begitu, hati-hati.

290
00:16:42,918 --> 00:16:45,295
Hei, kau sungguh berhenti bermain <i>ssireum?</i>

