Ada apa soal itu?

301
00:17:16,326 --> 00:17:18,078
Tidak jadi. Lupakan saja.

302
00:17:18,662 --> 00:17:20,873
Ada apa soal itu? Katakan saja.

303
00:17:23,167 --> 00:17:26,378
Berandal itu memang tahu
cara membuatku kesal.

304
00:17:29,548 --> 00:17:31,258
Kini dia membuatku penasaran.

305
00:17:42,895 --> 00:17:43,854
Itu untukku?

306
00:17:45,647 --> 00:17:47,649
Sedang apa dia di atas sana?

307
00:17:47,733 --> 00:17:49,318
Astaga.

308
00:17:49,902 --> 00:17:50,861
Sungguh aneh.

309
00:17:58,744 --> 00:18:01,914
Kenapa dia selalu membawa itu?

310
00:18:01,997 --> 00:18:06,877
Menurutku enam bulan.

311
00:18:07,753 --> 00:18:09,505
Percayalah.

312
00:18:09,588 --> 00:18:13,092
Dia akan tinggalkan Geosan
dalam enam bulan.

313
00:18:13,675 --> 00:18:16,261
Dia berwajah seperti orang kota
yang dingin.

314
00:18:16,345 --> 00:18:17,262
Apa aku salah?

315
00:18:17,346 --> 00:18:20,808
Dia memang tampak seperti hidup
di kota besar sejak lahir.

316
00:18:20,891 --> 00:18:24,228
Aku tak akan baik
pada orang seperti itu lagi.

317
00:18:24,311 --> 00:18:26,063
- Kenapa?
- Kau tak ingat?

318
00:18:27,022 --> 00:18:28,482
Pengantin baru itu

319
00:18:28,565 --> 00:18:30,734
berkata bertani adalah mimpi mereka.

320
00:18:31,985 --> 00:18:33,028
Aku ingat.

321
00:18:33,112 --> 00:18:37,491
Aku baik pada mereka. Ingat?

322
00:18:37,991 --> 00:18:43,163
Berpikir pasti mereka kesulitan
pindah kemari karena tak tahu apa pun.

323
00:18:43,247 --> 00:18:45,124
Aku banyak membantu mereka.

324
00:18:45,207 --> 00:18:47,042
- Benar.
- Bertani apanya.

325
00:18:47,126 --> 00:18:50,045
Hal yang mereka bisa hasilkan
hanyalah anak.

326
00:18:50,129 --> 00:18:52,005
Lalu mereka pergi ke Seoul.

327
00:18:52,089 --> 00:18:55,050
Mereka dapat hasil panen bagus di sini.

328
00:18:55,134 --> 00:18:57,553
Bukan hanya hasil panen bagus.

329
00:18:57,636 --> 00:18:59,972
Mereka dapat panen besar.

330
00:19:00,055 --> 00:19:02,516
- Panen besar.
- Astaga, nakalnya.

331
00:19:02,599 --> 00:19:05,936
Mereka hanya terus membuat anak.

332
00:19:07,688 --> 00:19:10,649
Mau minta dia datang
ke pertemuan warga hari ini?

333
00:19:10,732 --> 00:19:13,694
- Tidak, apa gunanya?
- Jangan.

334
00:19:18,490 --> 00:19:19,783
Halo.

335
00:19:23,620 --> 00:19:27,040
Bisa beri tahu aku di mana lokasi
pertemuan warga?

336
00:19:28,458 --> 00:19:30,919
Cobalah buat bundar.

337
00:19:31,003 --> 00:19:32,629
- Itu berlebihan.
- Apa?

338
00:19:32,713 --> 00:19:33,922
Itu terlalu banyak.

339
00:19:34,006 --> 00:19:36,216
Itukah alasannya tidak bundar?

340
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:38,427
Kalian pakai apa? Celemek?

341
00:19:39,052 --> 00:19:40,387
Kalian sedang apa?

342
00:19:40,470 --> 00:19:44,850
Pertemuan warga akan diadakan di sini.
Cuci tanganmu dan bergabunglah.

343
00:19:47,144 --> 00:19:48,520
- Hei!
- Aku…

344
00:19:48,604 --> 00:19:50,397
Berhentilah makan.

345
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:52,983
Kau makan dua, selagi kubuat satu.

346
00:19:53,066 --> 00:19:55,652
Jika begini, tak akan selesai tahun ini.

347
00:19:56,195 --> 00:19:59,781
Itu karena kau. Ingat?
Kau dan Baek-du makan ginseng merah,

348
00:19:59,865 --> 00:20:01,325
aku makan akar…

349
00:20:01,408 --> 00:20:03,243
Hei, Teman-Teman.

350
00:20:03,327 --> 00:20:06,246
Kalian ingat Du-sik teman masa kecil kita?

351
00:20:06,330 --> 00:20:07,789
Du-sik?

352
00:20:07,873 --> 00:20:10,751
- Putri Jun?
- Ya, dia.

353
00:20:10,834 --> 00:20:13,670
Kau serius? Aku tak mungkin lupa.

354
00:20:13,754 --> 00:20:16,798
Maka kau akan mengenalinya
jika melihatnya sekarang?

355
00:20:16,882 --> 00:20:17,883
Hei.

356
00:20:17,966 --> 00:20:20,928
Du-sik berwajah jelek…

357
00:20:21,511 --> 00:20:23,305
Maksudku, fitur wajahnya unik.

358
00:20:23,388 --> 00:20:26,391
Jadi, akan langsung kukenali
jika melihatnya.

359
00:20:26,475 --> 00:20:27,434
Begitukah?

360
00:20:28,143 --> 00:20:30,729
Bicara soal itu, tempo hari…

361
00:20:30,812 --> 00:20:33,523
Membahas Du-sik membuatku teringat.

362
00:20:33,607 --> 00:20:37,277
Lihat wanita yang pindah
ke tempat tinggal Du-sik dahulu?

363
00:20:37,361 --> 00:20:38,570
Ya.

364
00:20:38,654 --> 00:20:39,696
Konon dia cantik.

365
00:20:40,280 --> 00:20:41,406
- Apa?
- Kau yakin?

366
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:42,407
Aku yakin itu.

367
00:20:42,491 --> 00:20:43,700
Sungguh?

368
00:20:44,409 --> 00:20:45,661
- Begitukah?
- Mundur.

369
00:20:45,744 --> 00:20:47,996
Pertemuan warga hari ini.

370
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:50,540
Semua wanita di lingkungan ini datang?

371
00:20:54,002 --> 00:20:55,504
KIM TAE-BAEK

372
00:20:55,587 --> 00:20:57,839
Hei. Kau datang lebih awal.

373
00:20:57,923 --> 00:20:59,424
Hei, kau akhirnya datang.

374
00:21:01,134 --> 00:21:02,803
Halo, Nona-Nona.

375
00:21:05,305 --> 00:21:07,432
Maaf aku terlambat.

376
00:21:07,516 --> 00:21:08,684
Hei.

377
00:21:13,605 --> 00:21:15,357
Sekelompok pelanggan datang.

378
00:21:19,027 --> 00:21:20,988
Astaga, lihat jamuan ini.

379
00:21:21,989 --> 00:21:23,949
- Nikmatilah.
- Makanlah.

380
00:21:24,032 --> 00:21:25,158
Terima kasih.

381
00:21:25,242 --> 00:21:26,910
Kuharap kalian suka makanannya.

382
00:21:27,661 --> 00:21:29,997
Kenapa Baek-du ada di sini?

383
00:21:35,919 --> 00:21:36,962
Terima kasih.

384
00:21:37,045 --> 00:21:39,006
Nikmatilah. Bawa pulang sisanya.

385
00:21:40,215 --> 00:21:41,466
Makan yang banyak.

386
00:21:45,137 --> 00:21:46,471
Hei.

387
00:21:47,639 --> 00:21:49,516
Siapa namamu?

388
00:21:50,434 --> 00:21:51,560
Aku?

389
00:21:55,689 --> 00:21:56,523
Oh Yu-gyeong.

390
00:21:57,524 --> 00:22:00,277
Bisa bicara lebih keras?

391
00:22:04,281 --> 00:22:06,950
Oh Yu-gyeong.

392
00:22:08,243 --> 00:22:09,911
- Oh Yu-gyeong.
- Yu-gyeong?

393
00:22:12,247 --> 00:22:13,457
Oh Yu-gyeong.

394
00:22:14,333 --> 00:22:15,625
Apa katamu?

395
00:22:19,338 --> 00:22:20,547
Kenapa bertanya?

396
00:22:20,630 --> 00:22:23,467
Kenapa kau mau tahu
dari mana asal keluarganya?

397
00:22:24,134 --> 00:22:26,803
Hei, Yu-gyeong.

398
00:22:26,887 --> 00:22:29,306
Kenapa kau pindah kemari?

399
00:22:29,389 --> 00:22:31,975
Soal itu, aku…

400
00:22:33,477 --> 00:22:36,313
- Karena pekerjaan.
- Pekerjaan? Pekerjaan apa?

401
00:22:37,439 --> 00:22:38,607
Aku hanya…

402
00:22:40,275 --> 00:22:41,443
pegawai negeri.

403
00:22:41,526 --> 00:22:44,321
Di mana keluargamu? Sudah menikah?

404
00:22:44,404 --> 00:22:45,906
Kau di sini sendirian?

405
00:22:47,491 --> 00:22:48,575
Hei.

406
00:22:48,658 --> 00:22:51,286
Kau tanyakan hal pribadi.

407
00:22:51,369 --> 00:22:53,163
- Hentikan.
- Apa?

408
00:22:53,246 --> 00:22:56,666
Kita akan menjadi tetangga.

409
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:59,211
Kita bisa saling mengenal perlahan.

410
00:22:59,294 --> 00:23:01,713
Jangan terburu-buru. Paham?

411
00:23:01,797 --> 00:23:03,423
Cukup bertanyanya.

412
00:23:04,341 --> 00:23:08,345
Biar kubahas agenda pertemuan hari ini.

413
00:23:08,929 --> 00:23:12,933
Kalian tahu Seongdo-eup,
desa tetangga kita, 'kan?

414
00:23:13,016 --> 00:23:15,560
Kudengar seseorang tertabrak mobil kemarin

415
00:23:15,644 --> 00:23:17,896
dan terluka parah.

416
00:23:17,979 --> 00:23:19,606
Juga ada kecelakaan

417
00:23:19,689 --> 00:23:21,983
yang terjadi di sini tempo hari.

418
00:23:22,067 --> 00:23:24,444
- Jadi, aku…
- Benar.

419
00:23:24,528 --> 00:23:28,615
Aku lupa memberitahumu hal ini
mengenai itu.

